stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NotInstalled
    NotInstalled --> Initializing: POST /init
    Initializing --> Disabled: Resources created
    Disabled --> Enabled: POST /enable
    Enabled --> Disabled: POST /disable
    Enabled --> Enabled: Scoring task runs (1h)
    Enabled --> Enabled: POST /schedule_now
    Enabled --> Deleting: POST /dangerously_delete_data
    Disabled --> Deleting: POST /dangerously_delete_data
    Deleting --> NotInstalled: All data removed
